    "This very daunting computation can be carried out by automatic differentiation systems that can differentiate through the solution of a convex optimization problem, such as CVXPYlayers [AAB + 19, BAB20].",
    "In this section we present numerical experiments that illustrate the ideas and methods discussed above.",
    "In the first set of experiments, described in §5.2, we show the effect of several constraints and objective terms that serve as effective regularizers and improve performance.",
